name: Threads describing the cosmos #1 / Multimodal A.I Art / 7k Pixels
description:
Creating artistic images using machine learning tools, Antagonic Generative Network. These networks are a class of artificial intelligence algorithms that are used in unsupervised learning.

This technique can produce authentic looking human-made images.

By converting sentences into visual content, this AI can understand the context of the text through its perspective, and transform it into unique images.
